hadiths[24]{hadithnumber,text}:
1867,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Madina haram hai falan jagah se falan jagah tak (yani Jabal eir se Saur tak) us had mein koi darakht na kaataa jaey na koi bidat ki jaey aur jisne bhi yahan koi bidat nikaalii is par Allah Taala aur tamam malaaika aur insanon ki laanat hai.
1868,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Madina (hijrat karke) tashrif laey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid ki tameer ka hukm diya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey banu-Najjaar tum (apni us zameen ki) mujh se qeemat ley lo lekin unhon-ne kaha ke ham uski qeemat sirf Allah Taala se maangtey hain. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mushrekeen ki qabron ke mutaalliq farmaya aur wo ukhaad di gain, weeraana ke mutaalliq hukm diya aur wo barabar kar diya gaya, khajoor ke darakhton ke mutaalliq hukm diya aur wo kaat diye gaey aur wo darakht qible ki taraf bichhaa diye gaey."
1869,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Madina ke donon pathreeley kinaron mein jo zameen hai wo meri zaban par haram thahraaii gaee. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) banu- Harisa ke paas aaey aur farmaya banu-Haarisa! mera khayal hai ke tum log haram se bahar ho gaey ho, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mud kar dekha aur farmaya ke nahi balke tum log haram ke andar hi ho."
1870,"mere paas kitabullah aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us saheefe ke siwa jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se hai aur koi cheez (sharaee ehkaam se mutaalliq) likhi hui sura mein nahi hai. us saheefe mein ye bhi likha hua hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Madina Aair pahaadii se lekar falan maqam tak haram hai, jisne us had mein koi bidat nikaalii ya kisi bid'ati ko panah di to is par Allah aur tamam malaaika aur insanon ki laanat hai, na uski koi farz ibadat maqbool hai na nafl aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tamam musalmanon mein se kisi ka bhi ahad kafi hai isliye agar kisi musalman ki (dii hui aman mein doosrey musalman ne) bad-ahdii ki to is par Allah Taala aur tamam malaaika aur insanon ki laanat hai. na uski koi farz ibadat maqbool hai na nafl, aur jo koi apne Malik ko chhod kar uski ijazat ke baghair kisi doosrey ko Malik banaaey, is par Allah aur tamam malaaika aur insanon ki laanat hai, na uski koi farz ibadat maqbool hai na nafl."
1871,"maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey aik aisey Shahar (mein hijrat) ka hukm hua hai jo doosrey shehron ko kha lega. (yani sab ka sardaar banega) munaafeqeen usey yasrib kehtey hain lekin iska naam Madina hai wo (burey) logon ko is tarah bahar kar deta hai jis tarah bhattii lohey ke zang ko nikal deti hai."
1872,ham ghazwa Tabook se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath wapas hotey huey jab Madina ke qareeb pahunchey to aap ne farmaya ke ye taaba aa gaya.
1873,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they agar main Madina mein hiran chartey huey dekhun to unhein kabhi na chhedoon kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Madina ki zameen donon pathreeley maidaanon ke beech mein haram hai.
1874,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log Madina ko behtar haalat mein chhod jaogey phir wo aisa ujaad ho jaeyga ke phir wahan wahshii jaanwar, darind aur parind basney lagengey aur aakhir mein muzena ke 2 charwaahey Madina aaengey taake apni bakriyon ko haank ley jayen lekin wahan unhein sirf wahshii janwar nazar aaeingey aakhir saniyatul-wadaa' tak jab pahunchen gey to apne munh ke bal gir padengey."
1875,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke aap ne farmaya ke Yaman fateh hoga to log apni sawaariyon ko daudaatey huey laaengey aur apne ghar walon ko aur unko jo unki baat maan jaeinge sawar karke Madina se (waapas Yaman ko) ley jaeinge kash! unhein malum hota ke Madina hi unke liye behtar tha aur Iraq fateh hoga to kuchh log apni sawaariyon ko tez daudaatey huey laaengey aur apne ghar walon ko aur jo unki baat maanengey apne sath (iraaq waapas) ley jaaenge. kash! unhein malum hota ke Madina hi unke liye behtar tha.
1876,"ham se khubaib-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan ne, unse hafs-bin-Aasim ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (qiyamat ke qareeb) eman Madina mein is tarah simat aaeyga jaisey sanp simat kar apne bil mein aa jaya karta hai."
1877,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke Madina walon ke sath jo shakhs bhi faraib karega wo is tarah ghul jaeyga jaisey namak mein pani ghul jaya karta hai.
1878,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina ke mahallaat mein se aik mahal yani oonchey makan par chadhey phir farmaya ke jo kuchh mein dekh raha hun kya tumhen nazar aa raha hai? main boondon ke girney ki jagah ki tarah tumharey gharon par fitnon ke nazil honey ki jaghon ko dekh raha hun. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Mamar aur Sulaimaan-bin-Kaseer ne Zohri ke waaste se ki hai.
1879,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Madina par dajjal ka raub bhi nahi padega us daur mein Madina ke saat (7) darwazey hongey aur har darwazey par 2 Farishtey hongey.
1880,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Madina ke raston par Farishtey hain na usmein taaoon aa sakta hai na dajjaal.
1881,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi aisa Shahar nahi milega jisey dajjal paamaal na karega, siwaey Makka aur Madina ke, unke har rastey par saf basta Farishtey khadey hongey jo unki hifazat karengey phir Madina ki zameen teen martaba kaanpegii jis se eik-eik kaafir aur munafiq ko Allah Taala usmein se bahar kar dega."
1882,"ham se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dajjal ke mutaalliq aik lambi hadis bayan ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni hadis mein ye bhi farmaya tha ke dajjal Madina ki aik khaarii shor zameen tak pahunchega is par Madina mein daakhila to haram hoga. (Madina se) us din aik shakhs uski taraf nikal kar badhega, ye logon mein aik behtreen nek mard hoga ya (ye farmaya ke) buzurg tareen logon mein se hoga wo shakhs kahega ke main gawahi deta hun ke to wahi dajjal hai jiske mutaalliq hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne itlaa di thi. dajjal kahega kya main usey qatl karke phir zinda kar daalun to tum logon ko mere maamle mein koi shuba reh jaaeyga? iske hawaarii kahengey : nahi. chunanche dajjal unhein qatl karke phir zinda kar dega. jab dajjal unhein zinda kar dega to wo banda kahega b-khudaa ab to mujh ko pura haal malum ho gaya ke to hi dajjal hai dajjal kahega lao usey phir qatl kar dun lekin us martaba wo qaabu na pa sakega."
1883,"aik dehati ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar Islam par bait ki, doosrey din aaya to usey bukhar chadhaa hua tha kehney laga ke meri bait tod dijiye. teen baar usne yahi kaha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar kya phir farmaya ke Madina ki misal bhattii ki si hai ke mail kuchail ko door karke khalis jauhar ko nikhaar deti hai."
1884,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-Uhud ke liye nikley to jo log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they unmein se kuchh log wapas aagey (ye munaafeqeen they) phir kuchh ne to ye kaha ke ham chal kar unhein qatl kar dengey aur aik jamat ne kaha ke qatl na karna chahiye is par ye aayat nazil hui ( فما لكم في المنافقين فئتين‏ (aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ke Madina ( burey ( logon ko is tarah door kar deta hai jis tarah aag mail kuchail door kar deti hai.
1885,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Allaah! jitni Makka mein barkat ata farmai hai Madina mein us se dugnii barkat kar. Jarir ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Usman-bin-Umar ne Yunus ke waaste ke sath ki hai.
1886,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kabhi safar se wapas aatey aur Madina ki diiwaaron ko dekhtey to apni sawari tez farma detey aur agar kisi janwar ki pusht par hotey to Madina ki mohabbat mein usey aid lagaatey.
1887,"apne door waley makanon chhod kar masjide-Nabawi se qareeb iqamat ikhtiyar kar lein, lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye pasand na kya ke Madina ke kisi hisse se bhi rihaaish tark ki jaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey banu-Salma ! tum apne qadmon ka sawab nahi chahtey , chunanche banu- Salma ne (apni aslii iqamat gaah mein) rihaaish baqi rakhii."
1888,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mere ghar aur mere member ke darmyan ( wali jagah ( jannat ke baaghon mein se aik baagh hai aur mera member qiyamat ke din mere hauz ( kausar ( par hoga.
1889,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Abu-Bakar aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bukhar mein mubtala ho gaey, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) jab bukhar mein mubtala huey to ye sher padhtey : har aadmi apne ghar walon mein subah karta hai haalaanke uski maut uski jootii ke tasme se bhi zyada qareeb hai. aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ka jab bukhar utartaa to aap buland awaz se ye ashaar padhtey : kaash! mein aik raat Makka ki wadi mein guzaar sakta aur mere charon taraf izkhir aur Jaleel (ghaas) hotiin. kaash! aik din mein Majnaa ke pani par pahunchtaa aur kash! main shaamma aur Tufail ( pahadon ( ko dekh saktaa. kahaa ke aey mere Allah ! Sheba-bin-Rabee', Utba-bin-Rabeea aur Umayya-bin-Khalaf mardoodon par laanat kar. unhon-ne apne watan se us wabaa ki zameen mein nikala hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sun kar farmaya aey Allah ! hamarey dilon mein Madina ki mohabbat isi tarah paida kar de jis tarah Makka ki mohabbat hai balke us se bhi zyaada! aey Allaah! hamarey saa aur hamarey mud mein barkat ata farma aur Madina ki aab w hua hamarey liye sihate-khair kar de yahan ke bukhar ko Juhaifa mein bhej de. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke jab ham Madina aaey to ye Allah ki sabse zyada wabaa wali sar zameen thi. unhon-ne kaha Madina mein Bathaan naam ke aik naala se zaraa-zaraa bd-maza aur badbudar pani baha karta tha."
1890,"aey Allaah! mujhey apne rastey mein shahadat ata kar aur meri maut apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Shahar mein muqaddar kar de. ibne-Zareea' ne rooh-bin-Qaasim se, unhon-ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se, unhon-ne apni walida se, unhon-ne Hafsa-bint-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah suna tha, Hisham ne bayan kya, unse Zaid ne, unse unke walid ne, unse Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne ke maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna phir yahi hadis riwayat ki."
